Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.35,Default,Ivan,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zašto Hibičov mora da se vrati?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:35.18,Default,Olga,0,0,0,,{\an8}Odlaziš li?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:37.95,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ne znam šta će biti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.99,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Sledeći put, {\i0}Svemirska braća{\i1}:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.26,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Olga, Hibito i Gagarin".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:44.25,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Izvini, Olga.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.95,0:21:44.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Mr. Hibbit}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.41,Default,But,0,0,0,,Gosn. Hibit!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.05,0:21:55.37,Default,A,0,0,0,,Eto ih.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.75,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Jej!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.18,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Odosmo...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.18,0:22:04.89,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Gore.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.11,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Gore.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.97,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Gore.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.08,0:22:13.47,Default,But,0,0,0,,Ovde se ispoljio rezultat njegovog treninga sa zastavicama.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.78,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Jeste li svi spremni?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.78,0:22:24.30,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Moj nos mi govori da sledi lansiranje.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.31,0:22:27.49,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,To smo već znali.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.36,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Vidim ga...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.36,0:22:31.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Jej! Jej!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.79,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Kako su kul!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.50,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Izvoli.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.24,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Šta je sa ovim šlemom?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.06,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Previše je mali za moju glavu.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.63,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Ali prevazići ću ovo svojom snagom!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.00,0:22:54.14,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Nemoj da navlačiš šlem koji ti padne pod ruku, gorilo Badi!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.14,0:22:58.31,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Šlemovi su dizajnirani za svakog od nas posebno.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.92,0:23:00.44,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,B-Boli...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.66,0:23:04.32,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Hej, taj je moj.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.84,0:23:06.57,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Ništa, hajde da ga izvučemo.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.83,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Baš nam pravi probleme...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.66,Default,All,0,0,0,,Spremni...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.54,0:23:16.68,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Spasili ste me, narode!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.51,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Š-Šta je bilo, ljudi?
